Introduction

Black Level was a six-member boy group under VT Entertainment. They made their official debut on February 26, 2022 with the mini-album "New-Start."

On November 29th, 2022 BLACK LEVEL has announced that members Uin, Younghoon, Taeyoung, and Ze:U will be leaving the group to purse their idols dream separately. The group plans to reorganize and come back in the near future.
